@startuml SSD_RegisterEmployee
title SSD: UC3 - Register Employee

actor "Center Administrator" as Admin
participant ":System" as System

autonumber

activate Admin
Admin -> System: starts the registration of a new employee
activate System
System --> Admin: asks to select a role (Center Administrator, Nurse, Receptionist)
deactivate System

Admin -> System: selects the intended role
activate System
System --> Admin: requests mandatory data (Name, Phone, E-mail, Citizen Card Number)
deactivate System

Admin -> System: inputs the requested data
activate System

alt invalid data or duplicate
    System --> Admin: informs validation error (e.g., duplicate email/phone)
else valid data
    System --> Admin: confirms successful registration
end

deactivate System
deactivate Admin

@enduml